---

This software is an independent client for the HiQ LCA dataset editor. It is the
open local stdio MCP client that forwards business operations to the editor's
HTTP API and adds local file capabilities (UPR-template parsing, process export).
It does not contain the editor server's database schema, SQL, or business logic.
Names of background databases and standards referenced in the tool descriptions
(e.g. "Ecoinvent", "HiQLCD") are the trademarks of their respective owners and
are used only to describe the API surface this client talks to.
